attributeSource.infoString2: Berkshire Hathaway Homeservices Utah - Salt Lake

data.description: Located in the heart of Suncrest in close proximity to cafe/grocery.  Pool, Recreational Facilities, Large park with a soccer field, Basketball courts. Cable TV and internet are included in HOA dues. Close to commuting arteries. This gem of a home has all the upgrades & awaits the discerning buyer. This house has a fantastic million-dollar view of Utah Valley, Utah Lake, Suncrest Park, soccer field & Mountains. The Kitchen sports SS appliances, granite tops & gleaming slate flooring - a chef's delight. Convenient and beautiful main-floor Master. The large lower level/basement has 3 bedrooms, Livingroom, a wet bar, and 3 cold storage rooms. A French door walk-out to the backyard & daylight windows in all 3 basement bedrooms. What a value! Six total bedrooms, and a study/sitting area which can be easily converted to a seventh bedroom. Oversized 3 car garage with an RV parking spot. Central vacuum, Alarm system on all doors and windows, and more. New roof and air conditioner July 2022
data.whatILove: The 20-foot ceiling in the main Living room has 6 large windows to provide for a great million-dollar view.  From these windows, you can see the beautiful Suncrest Park and soccer field, most of Utah Lake, the cities below in Utah County, and the majestic Wasatch Mountain Range, including a beautiful view of Mt. Timpanogos. This house sits at a 6,300-foot elevation and the unobstructed view of the twinkling city lights below is remarkable.  On the 4th of July and on Pioneer Day you can see fireworks from multiple cities below us. A new roof and air conditioner was installed in July 2022.
